title: Fab! Vaani Kapoor On The Elle India January Cover
text: tweet After receiving accolades for her work in the movie Befikre , Vaani Kapoor has kicked off the new year by gracing the cover of Elle magazine. Easy, breezy and fabulous, Vaani slays it with a yellow strappy dress. With minimalistic make-up and the flawless attitude, she is all ready for the scorching summer sun. We think she looks stunning.
